---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
import DisclaimerBox from '../components/DisclaimerBox.astro';
import { SITE } from '../config';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="About ProfitPath"
  description="ProfitPath is an honest business reference: real startup costs, realistic earnings, and straight talk about difficulty and failure — with no courses to sell and no affiliate pressure."
  path="/about"
>
  <div class="container container-narrow page-head">
    <Breadcrumbs items={[{ label: 'Home', href: '/' }, { label: 'About' }]} />
    <h1>About ProfitPath</h1>
    <p class="lead">A serious, honest reference for anyone seriously considering starting a business.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="container container-narrow page-body">
    <h2>Why this site exists</h2>
    <p>
      Most "business ideas" content online is built to sell you something — a course, a coaching
      program, an affiliate link, or a dream. The numbers are cherry-picked, the failures are
      hidden, and the hard parts are glossed over. We built {SITE.name} to be the opposite: a
      practical reference that respects your intelligence and your real circumstances.
    </p>
    <p>
      Every business we cover gets the same honest treatment — what it actually costs to start,
      what it realistically earns, how long it really takes to see income, what skills it truly
      requires, and what most people get wrong when they try it. We show the full realistic range,
      not the best case. If a business is hard, capital-intensive, or fails often, we say so.
    </p>

    <h2>What makes us different</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Real startup costs</strong> — itemized and realistic, not estimates pulled from thin air.</li>
      <li><strong>Realistic earnings</strong> — based on reported data and operator accounts, not best-case scenarios.</li>
      <li><strong>Honest failure analysis</strong> — what goes wrong, why people quit, and how to avoid it.</li>
      <li><strong>No courses to sell</strong> — no upsells, no affiliate pressure, no "secret system."</li>
      <li><strong>Written for real constraints</strong> — real budgets, real time, real skills.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How we make money</h2>
    <p>
      We believe in being transparent about this. {SITE.name} is supported by advertising. We may
      display ads from advertising networks (such as Google AdSense) to keep the site free and
      independent. Ads are clearly labeled, kept away from the data and tools so they never confuse
      a financial decision, and never disguised as recommendations. We do not sell courses, and our
      business breakdowns are not influenced by advertisers.
    </p>

    <h2>Our standard</h2>
    <p>
      The measure of success for any page on this site is simple: when you finish reading, you
      should be able to say, "Now I actually know whether this is right for me, and exactly what I
      need to do to start." Everything we publish is built toward that moment.
    </p>
    <p>
      Want to know exactly how we put each page together? Read
      <a href="/how-we-research-businesses">how we research businesses</a> and our
      <a href="/data-sources">data sources</a>.
    </p>

    <div style="margin-top: 2rem;">
      <DisclaimerBox />
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
